healthcare.Description: The act of providing medical care to improve a person's well-being.

identity.Description: Identity verification related services to verify that end user submitted information is accurate and related to the identity of a genuine person.

platform.Description: The technology of computer systems that defines how a system is operated as a foundation, upon which other processes, application or technologies are developed.

supply-chain.Description: Supply chain refers to the system between a company and its supplier to produce and distribute a product to the end buyer.
